---
description: Testing standards and requirements
globs: ["**/*.test.*", "**/*.spec.*", "**/__tests__/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

Write unit tests for domain logic and custom hooks (Vitest + React Testing Library).
Integration tests for composite flows (component + hook + mocked adapters).
E2E for critical flows (Playwright/Cypress).
CI: typecheck + lint + unit tests on PR. New/changed code must include tests.
Tests must verify presence and meaningful assertions.
Use React Testing Library for rendering components in tests.
Mock custom hooks and stores when testing components.
